The New Turing Omnibus is expertly steered by one A.K. Dewdney, 
and has been for the last 20-odd years. Out the side windows 
one sees a comprehensive vista of computation's landmark'd plains.

Aaaaaaall aboard!!

Many of these sketchs will be graphical, and when they are, 
you'll be able to run them with Ruby-Processing.

Otherwise, vanilla Ruby should do the trick.